            <title>一加 Ace 5 Pro 手机支持「超远距灵动蓝牙」，蓝牙信号至多覆盖 400 米</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/819/377.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/819/377.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 06:50:14 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2158026" rel="nofollow">Autumn_Dream</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1933769" rel="nofollow">软媒新友1933769</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D795776" rel="nofollow">風見暉一</a> 的线索投递！</div>
